data.description: Are you looking for the classic older home with a lot of charm?? This home is on the outside of downtown, but close enough to stores, and the Pacific Ocean for the escape to watch the waves. Don't let this classic home pass you by, because you can be the next owner to love this home. MOTIVATED SELLERS. WILL LOOK AT ALL REASONABLE OFFERS.
